queryResponse.sql:
-- raw sql results do not include filled-in values for 'last_delivery.created_week'


SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "last_delivery_region.name") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN (CASE WHEN "shipments.shipment_count" IS NOT NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) ELSE 2 END, CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN "shipments.shipment_count" ELSE NULL END DESC, "shipments.shipment_count" DESC, z__pivot_col_rank, "last_delivery_region.name") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "last_delivery.created_week" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "last_delivery.created_week") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS "last_delivery.created_week",
    last_delivery_region.name  AS "last_delivery_region.name",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (coalesce(first_pickup.is_drop_trailer or last_delivery.is_drop_trailer, false)) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_drop_count",
            (COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (((CASE
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_backup'  THEN 'Backup/Published'
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'
WHEN coalesce(shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'spot', true)  THEN 'Spot'

END) = 'Contract')) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) + COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (((CASE
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_backup'  THEN 'Backup/Published'
WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'
WHEN coalesce(shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'spot', true)  THEN 'Spot'

END) = 'Backup/Published')) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END)) / nullif(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END), 0) AS "shipments.percent_shipments_contract"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS first_pickup ON first_pickup.shipment_id=shipments.id and first_pickup.first_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(first_pickup.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS last_delivery ON last_delivery.shipment_id=shipments.id and last_delivery.last_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.lk_regions  AS last_delivery_region ON last_delivery_region.state_code=(upper(trim(last_delivery.state_code)))
WHERE ((( last_delivery.created_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', -14, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( last_delivery.created_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', 21, DATEADD('day', -14, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 500 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank

WHEN shipments.shipper_rate_type = 'contract_primary' or shipments.priced_under_contract = 'true' THEN 'Contract'

) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END), 0) AS "shipments.percent_shipments_contract"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments

LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.lk_regions  AS last_delivery_region ON last_delivery_region.state_code=(upper(trim(last_delivery.state_code)))
WHERE ((( last_delivery.created_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', -14, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( last_delivery.created_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', 21, DATEADD('day', -14, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    1
ORDER BY
    2 DESC
FETCH NEXT 30000 ROWS ONLY

SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "last_delivery.created_week" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "last_delivery.created_week") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (

    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END

    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (coalesce(first_pickup.is_drop_trailer or last_delivery.is_drop_trailer, false)) AND ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
